snippet.title: Darksiders Genesis - Official Strife Cinematic Trailer
snippet.description:
This new cinematic Darksiders Genesis trailer shows a very confident Strife going toe to toe with Hell itself. Darksiders Genesis just announced its Xbox and PS4 release date, which is February 14, 2020.  Pre-order at https://darksiders.com/order-here/

#ign
